As a fan of football, I've recently gotten annoyed with the way people use statistics to evaluate NFL kickers. To illustrate what I'm talking about, take a look at this table of field goal stats from ESPN.com for the 2018 season and try to answer this question: who was the best kicker in the NFL this season?



 
